去睇,如果你要屌,可能成世都屌唔嗮.<br />\n<br />\n不要太認真.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">咁只係代表你ignorant而唔係串</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你好難叫一個廿五歲嘅習慣同一班15，16歲嘅玩</span><br />\n<br />\n不要太認真就認同嘅。<br />\n<br />\n我本身都唔會太認真，我只係希望連登可以變返有質素少少啫，有時真係想認真討論但總有班on9喺度阻住囇。"},{"pid":"32f8e46291c7cdd11b09d55aefd10b3aed14a9d4","tid":432741,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T20:42:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cbcf023e63e08137caae1b90a7886aade1f785f","tid":432741,"uid":147022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T20:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得呢度低質你咪走囉，連登唔適合你上。<br />\n又要上又要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想你地走多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你想連登得番你自己單機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIQ低過100嘅走哂我諗都仲會有一半人嘅"},{"pid":"aef9759414cafe6da10347611f34cecea098d745","tid":432741,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T20:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/045723_4635f5e0a2619544a36dd617708ccd62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F045723_4635f5e0a2619544a36dd617708ccd62.jpg&h=b1b2e191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過可能人地都唔想生活喺台灣？可能人地都係反緊中共？<br />\n<br />\n理性d啦唔該。你地呢種言論上到國際都係會引起公憤，咁只會比多樣野大陸人批評我地。<br />\n<br />\n唉，上連登真係好撚辛苦。"},{"pid":"a3e12e73508161c9e46cbaba85cbf8cdc8fd97af","tid":432741,"uid":147022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T21:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/045723_4635f5e0a2619544a36dd617708ccd62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.es